<section xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
	<title>Dynamic Interface Adapter</title>
	<para>
Header <filename>dynamic_adapter.hpp</filename>.
	</para>
<programlisting role="cpp"><![CDATA[template<class Interface, class Part = Interface>
class dynamic_adapter
{
};]]></programlisting>
<programlisting role="cpp"><![CDATA[template<class Interface, class Part, class Parent>
class dynamic_adapter_base: dynamic_adapter<Interface, Parent>
{
};]]></programlisting>
	<para>
Specialize <emphasis>dynamic_adapter&lt;Interface, Base&gt;</emphasis> to 
override methods of the <emphasis>Interface</emphasis> and then make this 
adapter as a base type of an implementation.
	</para>
</section>
